==Getting started==
===Talking to Khazard Guard at the east entrance==={{^|id=1208,1209 without Khazard armour}}
* '''Player:''' Hello.
* '''Khazard Guard:''' This area is restricted, leave now!
* '''Khazard Guard:''' OUT! And don't come back.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Khazard Guard around the Fight Arena==={{^|id=1211}}
* '''Player:''' Hello.
* '''Khazard Guard:''' I don't know you stranger. Get off our land.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Local===
* '''Player:''' Hello.
* '''Local:''' Hello stranger, are you new to these parts? You look lost.
* '''Local:''' I suppose you're here for the fight arena? There are some rich folk fighting tomorrow. Should be entertaining.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Lady Servil===
* '''Player:''' Hi there. Looks like you're in some trouble.
* '''Lady Servil:''' Oh I wish this broken cart was my only problem... I've got to find my family...
* {{tselect|Start the Fight Arena quest?}}
* {{topt|Yes.}}
** '''Player:''' Can I help you?
** '''Lady Servil:''' Would you? Please?
** '''Lady Servil:''' I'm Lady Servil, my husband is Sir Servil. We were travelling north together with our son Sammy when we were ambushed by General Khazard's men.
** '''Player:''' General Khazard?
** '''Lady Servil:''' He's been after me ever since I declined his hand in marriage.
** '''Lady Servil:''' Now he's kidnapped my husband and son to fight in his battle arena to the south of here. I hate to think what he'll do to them. He's a sick and twisted man.
** '''Player:''' I'll try my best to return your family.
** '''Lady Servil:''' Please do. My family is wealthy and can reward you handsomely. I'll be waiting here for you.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|No.}}
** '''Player:''' I hope you can, good luck.
** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Lady Servil after starting the quest===
* '''Player:''' Hello Lady Servil.
* '''Lady Servil:''' Brave traveller, please... bring back my family.
* {{tact|end}}

==Entering the arena==
===Talking to Khazard Guard by the armour chest==={{^|id=1210}}
* '''Player:''' Hi.
* '''Khazard Guard:''' Who goes there?
* '''Player:''' Er... I... um...
* '''Khazard Guard:''' I don't know who you are. Get out of my house stranger.
* {{tact|end}}

===Opening the armour chest===
* {{mes|You open the chest.}}

===Searching the armour chest===
* {{tcond|If the player has neither helmet nor armour:}}
** {{tbox|You search the chest, and find the helmet and armour of a Khazard guard.}}{{^|Drops to ground with full inventory in all branches.}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player does not have the armour:}}
** {{tbox|You search the chest, and find the armour of a Khazard guard.}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player does not have the helmet:}}
** {{tbox|You search the chest, and find the helmet of a Khazard guard.}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player has both helmt and armour:}}
** {{mes|You search the chest, but find nothing.}}
** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Lady Servil after getting armour===
* '''Player:''' Hello Lady Servil.
* '''Lady Servil:''' Have you had any luck with freeing my family?
* '''Player:''' I've managed to get a guard's uniform, hopefully I can infiltrate the arena.
* '''Lady Servil:''' Please hurry.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Khazard Guard by the armour chest with Khazard armour equipped==={{^|id=1210}}
* '''Player:''' Hello.
* '''Khazard Guard:''' Despicable thieving scum, that was good armour. Did you see anyone around here soldier?
* '''Player:''' Me? No, no one!
* '''Khazard Guard:''' Hmmmm.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Khazard Guard around the fight arena with Khazard armour equipped==={{^|id=1211}}
* '''Player:''' Hello.
* '''Khazard Guard:''' Can I help you stranger?
* '''Khazard Guard:''' Oh, you're a guard as well. That's ok then. We don't like strangers around here.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Local after getting the armour==={{^|armour need not be equipped}}
* '''Player:''' Hello.
* '''Local:''' I heard the Servil family are fighting soon. Should be very entertaining.
* '''Local:''' Hello stranger, are you new to these parts?
* '''Player:''' I suppose I am.
* '''Local:''' What's your business?
* '''Player:''' Just visiting friends in the cells.
* '''Local:''' Visiting, that's funny.
* '''Local:''' Only Khazard guards are allowed to see prisoners. Unless you know where to get some Khazard armour, you won't be visiting anyone.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Khazard barman===
* '''Player:''' Hello.
* '''Khazard barman:''' Hi, what can I get you? We have a range of quality brews.
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|I'll have a beer please.}}
** '''Player:''' I'll have a beer please.
** '''Khazard barman:''' That'll be two gold coins please.
** {{tcond|If the player doesn't have 2 coins:}}
*** '''Player:''' Oh, I don't have enough money with me.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{tcond|If the player has 2 coins:}}
*** '''Khazard barman:''' There you go, that's two gold coins.{{^|Drops to ground with full inventory.}}
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|Got any news?}}
** '''Player:''' Got any news?
** '''Khazard barman:''' If you want to see the action around here you should visit the famous Khazard fight arena. I've seen some grand battles in my time. Ogres, goblins, even dragons have fought there.
** '''Khazard barman:''' Although you have to feel sorry for some of the slaves sent in there.
** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Khazard Guard inside the building with Khazard armour equipped==={{^|id=1208}}
* '''Player:''' Hello.
* '''Khazard Guard:''' I've never seen you around here before!
* '''Player:''' Long live General Khazard!
* '''Khazard Guard:''' Erm.. yes.. soldier, I take it you're new around here?
* '''Player:''' You could say that.
* '''Khazard Guard:''' Khazard died two hundred years ago. However his dark spirit remains in the form of the undead maniac General Khazard. Remember he is your master, always watching.
* '''Khazard Guard:''' Got that newbie?
* '''Player:''' Undead, maniac, master. Got it, loud and clear.
* {{tact|end}}

===Opening door while a Khazard Guard is nearby===
* '''Player:''' This door appears to be locked.
* '''Khazard Guard:''' Nice observation guard. You could have just asked to be let in like a normal person.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Joe===
* {{tcond|If the player has the Khazard armour equipped:}}
** '''Player:''' Do either of you know a Justin or Sammy Servil?
** '''Joe:''' If we did, why would we tell you guard?
** '''Kelvin:''' Until our last breath, our every action will be against Khazard. Never will we help you.
** '''Joe:''' I spit on Khazard's grave, and all who do his bidding.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player does not have the Khazard armour equipped:}}
** '''Player:''' Do either of you know a Justin or Sammy Servil?
** '''Joe:''' I have heard of those of whom you speak. But I fear it may be too late.
** '''Kelvin:''' It is said that Khazard has a personal vendetta against those two, their time is therefore short.
** '''Joe:''' You're a brave [man/woman]. If the guards get you, you'll be in here next.
** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Kelvin===
* {{tcond|If the player has the Khazard armour equipped:}}
** '''Player:''' Do either of you know a Justin or Sammy Servil?
** '''Kelvin:''' If we did, why would we tell you guard?
** '''Joe:''' Until our last breath, our every action will be against Khazard. Never will we help you.
** '''Kelvin:''' I spit on Khazard's grave, and all who do his bidding.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player does not have the Khazard armour equipped:}}
** '''Kelvin:''' I have heard of those of whom you speak. But I fear it may be too late.
** '''Joe:''' It is said that Khazard has a personal vendetta against those two, their time is therefore short.
** '''Kelvin:''' You're a brave [man/woman]. If the guards get you, you'll be in here next.
** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Fightslave===
* '''Player:''' Do you know of a Justin or Sammy Servil in this arena?
* {{tcond|If the player has the Khazard armour equipped:}}
** '''Fightslave:''' Please leave me alone.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player does not have the Khazard armour equipped:}}
** '''Fightslave:''' I've not met anybody in here by that name.
** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Hengrad===
* '''Player:''' Do you know a Justin or Sammy Servil?
* '''Hengrad:''' You're not a real guard. I've been in here long enough to know that. What's your business?
* '''Player:''' I've been sent to rescue Sir Servil and his son.
* '''Hengrad:''' I've seen them in here, although they don't look up to much. My advice to you is to leave before you end up in a cell too.
* {{tact|end}}

===Opening door to the arena===
* {{tcond|If the nearby guards are alive:}}
** '''Khazard Guard:''' And where do you think you're going? Only General Khazard decides who fights in the arena. Get out of here.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the nearby guards are dead:}}
** {{mes|This door appears to be locked.}}
** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to drunk Khazard Guard with Khazard armour equipped==={{^|id=1209}}
* '''Player:''' Long live General Khazard!
* '''Khazard Guard:''' Erm.. yes.. quite right.
* '''Khazard Guard:''' Have you come to laugh at the fight slaves? I used to really enjoy it, but after a while they become quite boring.
* '''Khazard Guard:''' Now I just want a decent drink. Mind you, too much Khali brew and I'll fall asleep.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to drunk Khazard Guard again with Khazard armour equipped==={{^|id=1209}}
* '''Player:''' Hello again.
* '''Khazard Guard:''' Bored, bored, bored. You'd think the slaves would be more entertaining. Selfish the lot of them.
* '''Khazard Guard:''' I used to enjoy this job, but now all I want is a decent drink.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Sammy Servil===
* '''Player:''' Hello.
* '''Sammy Servil:''' Please Sir, don't hurt me.
* {{tcond|If the player has the Khazard armour equipped:}}
** '''Player:''' Sshh. This uniform is a disguise, I'm here to help. Where do they keep the keys?
* {{tcond|If the player does not have the Khazard armour equipped:}}
** '''Player:''' Sshh. I'm here to help. Where do they keep the keys?
* '''Sammy Servil:''' The guard always keeps hold of them.
* '''Player:''' Don't lose heart, I'll be back.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Lady Servil after entering the arena===
* '''Player:''' Lady Servil, I have managed to infiltrate General Khazard's arena.
* '''Lady Servil:''' And my family?
* '''Player:''' I'm working on it.
* '''Lady Servil:''' Please hurry.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Khazard barman after learning about the Khali brew===
* '''Player:''' Hello.
* '''Khazard barman:''' Hi, what can I get you? We have a range of quality brews.
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|I'll have a beer please.}}
** {{tact|above}}
* {{topt|I'd like a Khali brew please.}}
** '''Player:''' I'd like a Khali brew please.
** '''Khazard barman:''' That'll be five gold coins please.
** {{tcond|If the player doesn't have 5 coins:}}
*** '''Player:''' Oh, I don't have enough money with me.
*** {{tact|end}}
** '''Khazard barman:''' There you go, that's five gold coins. I suggest lying down before you drink it. That way you have less distance to collapse.{{^|Drops to ground with full inventory.}}
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|Got any news?}}
** {{tact|above}}

===Talking to drunk Khazard Guard while holding Khali brew==={{^|id=1209}}
* '''Player:''' Hello again.
* '''Khazard Guard:''' Bored, bored, bored. You'd think the slaves would be more entertaining. Selfish the lot of them.* '''Player:''' Do you still fancy a drink?
* '''Khazard Guard:''' I really shouldn't... oh... ok then just the one.
* {{tbox|You hand a bottle of Khali brew to the guard. He takes a mouthful of the drink.}}
* '''Khazard Guard:''' Blimey this stuff is pretty good. It's not too strong is it?
* '''Player:''' No, not at all. You'll be fine.
* {{tbox|The guard quickly finishes the rest of the bottle and begins to sway slightly.}}
* '''Khazard Guard:''' That is some gooood stuff... yeah... wooh yeah!
* '''Player:''' Are you alright?
* '''Khazard Guard:''' Yeesshh, hiccup! Oooh, maybe I sshould relax for a while.
* '''Player:''' Good idea. I'll look after the prisoners.
* '''Khazard Guard:''' Yeesh, yes that shounds reasonable. Here, 'hiccup', take the keysch. Any trouble, you give... you givem a good beating.
* '''Player:''' No problem, I'll keep them in line.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to drunk Khazard Guard after getting the keys===
* '''Player:''' Hello, how's the job?
* '''Khazard Guard:''' Please, leave me alone. I'm sure the walls never used to sway that much.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to drunk Khazard Guard after losing the keys===
* '''Player:''' Hi, er.. I lost the keys.
* '''Khazard Guard:''' What?!  You're foolish...
* '''Khazard Guard:''' ...and I'm drunk. Here, take my spare set.{{^|Drops to floor with full inventory.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to drunk Khazard Guard after getting him drunk without Khazard armour equipped===
* '''Player:''' Hello.
* '''Khazard Guard:''' Go away. Thish areash resh... restricted! We don't like strangersh, 'specially ones who sway. Oooh!
* {{tact|end}}

===Using keys on a cell that does not contain Sammy Servil===
* '''Player:''' The gate is locked, but Sammy's not in there anyway.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Sammy Servil after getting the keys===
* '''Player:''' Sammy look, I have the keys.
* '''Sammy Servil:''' Wow! Please set me free, then we can find my dad. I overheard a guard talking. I think they've taken him to the arena.
* '''Player:''' Ok, we'd better hurry.
* {{qact|The player unlocks the door.}}
* '''Sammy Servil:''' {{overhead|I'll run ahead.}}
* '''Player:''' Sammy, where's your father?
* '''Sammy Servil:''' Quick, help him! That beast will kill him. He's too old to fight.
* {{qact|A cutscene plays of a Khazard Ogre exiting a cell toward Justin Servil.}}
* {{tact|end}}

==The battles==
===Talking to Sammy Servil in the arena===
* '''Player:''' Sammy, where's your father?
* '''Sammy Servil:''' Quick, help him! That beast will kill him. He's too old to fight.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to General Khazard===
* {{tcond|If the player has the Khazard armour equipped:}}
** '''Player:''' General Khazard?
** '''General Khazard:''' What do you want guard? I'm a busy man.
** '''Player:''' Of course sir.
** '''General Khazard:''' In the last two hundred years, I have survived all horrors imaginable. Now it is my turn to cover this land in darkness. One day you shall see, all will quake on hearing my name.
** '''General Khazard:''' Now leave me.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player does not have the Khazard armour equipped:}}
** '''General Khazard:''' Who dares enter my home? You? A feeble traveller?
** '''Player:''' Feeble?!
** '''General Khazard:''' Get out!  Whoever let you in shall be severely punished for this.
** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Justin Servil===
* '''Player:''' Lady Servil sent me to rescue you and your son. Come on, we have to get out of here.
* '''Justin Servil:''' I'm too old to fight. I'm afraid you'll have to kill that ogre by yourself.
* {{tact|end}}

===Trying to exit the arena through the door===
* '''Sammy Servil:''' Please don't go, you must help us. We'll never survive in here alone.
* '''Player:''' Where's your father Sammy?
* '''Sammy Servil:''' Quick, help him! That beast will kill him. He's too old to fight.
* {{tact|end}}

===Attacking General Khazard===
* {{mes|I don't have time. I'm here to rescue Sir Servil and Sammy.}}

===Talking to Lady Servil after freeing Sammy from the jail===
* '''Player:''' Lady Servil. I freed your son, however he has returned to the arena to help your husband.
* '''Lady Servil:''' Oh no, they won't stand a chance. Please go back and help.
* {{tact|end}}

