* '''Player:''' They belong to nobody.
* '''General Khazard:''' Well, I suppose we could find some arrangement for their freedom... hmmm?
* '''Player:''' What do you mean?
* '''General Khazard:''' I'll let them go, but you must stay and fight for me. You'll make me double the gold if you manage to last a few fights.
* '''General Khazard:''' Guards! Take [him/her] to the cells.
* {{qact|The player is taken to a jail cell.}}
* '''Khazard Guard:''' The General seems to have taken a liking to you. He'd normally kill imposters like you without a second thought.
* {{tact|end}}

