===Talking to Hengrad in the jail cell===
* '''Player:''' Are you ok stranger?
* '''Hengrad:''' I'm fine thanks.
* '''Hengrad:''' So Khazard got his hands on you too?
* '''Player:''' I'm afraid so.
* '''Hengrad:''' If you're lucky you may last as long as me.
* '''Player:''' How long have you been here?
* '''Hengrad:''' I've been in Khazard's prisons ever since I can remember. I was a child when his men kidnapped me. My whole life has been spent killing and fighting, all in the hope that one day I might escape.
* '''Player:''' Don't give up.
* '''Hengrad:''' Thanks friend.
* '''Hengrad:''' Wait.. sshh, the guard is coming. Looks like you'll be going into the arena. Good luck friend.
* {{qact|The guard walks up and unlocks the cell.}}
