* {{qact|The player is brought into the arena.}}
* {{tbox|From above you hear a voice.....  'Ladies and gentlemen! Let today's first fight between the outsider and everyone's favourite scorpion commence.'}}
* {{qact|The scorpion exits the cell and attacks the player.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Entering the building after starting the scorpion fight===
* '''Player:''' This door appears to be locked.
* '''Khazard Guard:''' So you're back for more are you? General Khazard will be pleased.
* {{tact|(The player is taken directly to the arena.)}}

===Talking to Sammy Servil in the arena during the scorpion fight===
* '''Player:''' Don't worry, I'll get us out of here.
* '''Sammy Servil:''' Thanks traveller. I'm sorry that you too are now a subject of this arena.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Justin Servil in the arena during the scorpion fight===
* '''Player:''' Don't worry, I'll get us out of here.
* '''Justin Servil:''' You've incurred the anger of Khazard yourself now. He won't let any of us go easily.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to General Khazard during the scorpion fight===
* '''Player:''' Hello.
* '''General Khazard:''' How dare you speak to me, you are a slave of this arena now.
* {{tact|end}}

===Trying to exit the arena during the scorpion fight===
* '''Khazard Guard:''' It would be impolite to leave now. The General insists you stay a little longer.
* {{tact|end}}

===Upon killing the scorpion===
* '''General Khazard:''' Not bad, not bad at all. I think you need a tougher challenge. Time for my puppy. Guards! Guards! Bring on Bouncer!
* {{tbox|From above you hear a voice.....  'Ladies and gentlemen! Today's second round of battle is between the outsider and Bouncer.'}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Justin Servil during the Bouncer fight===
* '''Player:''' Come on, we only have to fight a creature called bouncer now.
* '''Justin Servil:''' You may laugh, but the name of the General's 'pet' is feared by many in this land.
* '''Player:''' Don't worry, I'll get us out of here.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to the Local during the Bouncer fight===
* '''Player:''' Hello.
* '''Local:''' Hey you're the guy from the arena! How'd you get out!
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Hengrad during the Bouncer fight===
* '''Player:''' Hello again.
* '''Hengrad:''' I don't know how you managed to escape the arena, but you may not be as lucky next time. Get out of here while you can.
* {{tact|end}}

===Upon killing Bouncer===
* '''General Khazard:''' Nooooo! Bouncer! How dare you? You've taken the life of my only friend. Now you'll suffer traveller, prepare to meet your maker.
* '''Player:''' You agreed to let the Servils go if I stayed to fight.
* '''General Khazard:''' Indeed. I obviously underestimated you, although you still pale in comparison to the might of General Khazard.
* '''General Khazard:''' You shall see that I am not cowardly enough to make false promises. They may go.
* '''General Khazard:''' You however have caused me much trouble today. You must remain here so that I may at least have the pleasure of killing you myself.
* {{qact|General Khazard attacks the player.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Justin Servil after killing Bouncer===
* '''Player:''' What does Khazard want with us now?
* '''Justin Servil:''' I don't know, but I can't imagine he'll be happy with you now.
* '''General Khazard:''' The agreement was that the Servils may leave if you won a few fights, and indeed they are now free to do so.
* {{tact|above}}

===Talking to Sammy Servil after killing Bouncer===
* '''Player:''' What does Khazard want with us now?
* '''Sammy Servil:''' I don't know, but he won't be happy that you've killed his so called pet.
* '''General Khazard:''' The agreement was that the Servils may leave if you won a few fights, and indeed they are now free to do so.
* {{tact|above}}

===Talking to Justin Servil after General Khazard attacks===
* '''Player:''' You can run, Khazard's interest is in me now.
* '''Justin Servil:''' My thanks, we'll be ok now. I suggest you run too, General Khazard is mighty and his anger fearsome.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Sammy Servil after General Khazard attacks===
* '''Player:''' You and your father should run, Khazard's interest is in me now.
* '''Sammy Servil:''' I'm sorry to have gotten you into so much trouble. You should run as well, Khazard is too dangerous.
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to General Khazard after he attacks===
* '''Player:''' Hello.
* '''General Khazard:''' You killed my pet, and yet still you dare to speak to me?
* '''General Khazard:''' {{overhead|You shall die for your insolence.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Entering the door to the building after Khazard attacks===
* '''Player:''' This door appears to be locked.
* '''Khazard Guard:''' You're [him/her]. The one who murdered the General's pet.
